    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a superlative example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is offered in showroom condition, having undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards. With its flawless finish and impeccable mechanical integrity, this specimen represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector. It remains, quite simply, without peer in the current market.",
