      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly so excited to find a new home for this absolute gem. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, and it\u2019s in such incredible shape\u2014it truly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been super meticulous with its care, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road for its next adventure. You\u2019ve got to see it in person to believe how clean it is. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
