    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example of the legendary S54 platform. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six remains internally pristine, with the critical rod bearing service and VANOS overhaul already completed to factory specifications. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to the rear wheels via a perfectly functioning M-Variable differential. The chassis is structurally flawless, featuring proactive subframe reinforcement and a suspension geometry that retains its original rigidity. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior exhibits zero clear coat failure or panel misalignment, while the undercarriage remains dry and free of fluid seepage or oxidation. This is a turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
